    <p>
The 
              <xref outputclass="supportingInformation" keyref="supporting_definition_national_health_service_act_2006">National Health Service Act 2006</xref>
 received Royal Assent on 8 November 2006 and came into effect on 1 March 2007.        </p>
    <p>
The 
              <xref outputclass="supportingInformation" keyref="supporting_definition_national_health_service_act_2006">National Health Service Act 2006</xref>
 was significantly altered by the Health and Social Care Act 2012.        </p>
